    <item>
      <title>沃尔沃汽车因关税拖累和电动汽车普及放缓而缩减目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/volvo-car-pares-back-targets-on-tariff-drag-slow-ev-uptake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于关税上调对其在中国生产的部分车型造成冲击，沃尔沃汽车公司下调了预期，此前一天该公司放弃了到 2030 年只销售电动汽车的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/volvo-car-pares-back-targets-on-tariff-drag-slow-ev-uptake</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 06:27:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>达斯称印度经济数据放缓不会影响印度储备银行实现目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/rbi-s-das-sticks-to-7-2-growth-forecast-price-stability-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行行长沙克提坎塔·达斯表示，尽管上个季度经济放缓，但印度央行仍将维持本财年 7.2% 的经济增长预测，官员们将继续关注价格稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/rbi-s-das-sticks-to-7-2-growth-forecast-price-stability-focus</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 06:09:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员希望通过长期日元押注来规避工资单风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/traders-look-to-dodge-payroll-perils-with-specialized-yen-wagers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一小部分交易员正在进行极端的货币期权押注，旨在避开即将公布的美国就业数据带来的波动，而日元则是该策略的核心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/traders-look-to-dodge-payroll-perils-with-specialized-yen-wagers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 05:59:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>钢铁集团警告复苏“昙花一现” 铁矿石价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/iron-ore-hits-lowest-since-2022-as-industry-group-warns-on-steel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铁矿石价格跌至 2022 年以来的最低水平，交易价格接近每吨 90 美元，因为中国主要钢铁行业组织建议钢厂谨慎过快提高产量，以免扼杀夏季后的复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/iron-ore-hits-lowest-since-2022-as-industry-group-warns-on-steel</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 02:20:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
